{"tid":465075,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴司機位裝膠板防受襲","createTime":"2017-11-11T07:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T14:31:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8f93c19060984f7ccc0e3b9105544a7a21ffea","tid":465075,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171111/20210933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F20210933&d=CeERpCKrFVwiV386tkw2u5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=4fb072dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F20210933&h=53d603c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171111/20210933</a><br />\n<br />\n九巴司機位裝膠板防受襲<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171111/large/a0304a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171111%2Flarge%2Fa0304a.gif&h=ade435a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴試驗於司機位裝膠板，稱防花、防爆。九巴fb直播截圖<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】巴士司機遇襲事件近期屢見不鮮。九巴昨日透過fb專頁，直播介紹在司機位加裝膠板措施。九巴策劃及發展部襄理梁領彥指，近月有車長受襲和受到滋擾，經過多月設計和研究，決定試驗在巴士駕駛座位旁加裝膠板，保障司機安全。<br />\n膠板以高質素物料製造，可防花、防爆。直播期間，梁坐上駕駛座，另一名九巴人員則扮施襲者，不斷拍打膠板，梁稱：「塊膠板就可以成為第一道防線。」梁又指，加裝膠板是無可奈何，僅試驗性質的臨時措施。他稱：「如果乘客尊重車長，讓車長安心的話，長遠希望塊板唔會擺好耐。」<br />\n<br />\n九巴職員權益工會理事長李國華則認為，膠板既不是完全密封阻隔車長和乘客，卻阻礙車長活動，認為塊板「冇乜用」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅繼盛"},{"pid":"ac7168df3279c22c8a090a10fe123f9f92ffb1a3","tid":465075,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"類似深圳的士裝隔開司機和郵乘客的牆"},{"pid":"84fa214b15d0af0b8bd096b1aee7a039b442aead","tid":465075,"uid":28913,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"屌啦星, 民智倒退既反映"},{"pid":"7f98677a2d564c132c3bbeb16b19338d23